title: Wall Street Breakfast: The Week Ahead
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: The U.S. jobs report for June is expected to show promising figures, nearly back at pre-pandemic levels. Denim giants Levi Strauss (LEVI) will report earnings, following a sharp drop in share prices. And, even with less content on the big screen, cinemas are full and the summer 2022 box office continues to surpass expectations.
